<div id="c842" class="frame frame-default frame-type-text frame-layout-0"><header><h1 class="">
				ConfTool: Conference Management Software
			</h1></header><p>You are going to organize a conference and are looking for professional and efficient software for:</p><ul><li>the submission and review process of contributions,</li><li>the scheduling of the conference program,</li><li>the registration, administration and invoicing of participants,</li><li>and many other of the tasks of the organizer?</li></ul><p>ConfTool is a Web-based event management system developed to support the organization of academic conferences, workshops, congresses and seminars. It has&nbsp;helped more than <a href="/en/references.html" title="Opens internal link in current window">1000 organizers</a> to make their events a success and is<br /> available in over <a href="/en/demo_installations.html" title="Opens internal link in current window">10 languages</a>:&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_english_07.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;<img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_german_04.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_french_04.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_italian_04.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_spanish_06.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_catalan_05.gif.gif" width="20" height="14" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_portuguese_pt_03.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_portuguese_br.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_polish_04.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_russian_04.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_hungarian_02.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/romania.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_czech.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_slovak_04.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_slovenian_06.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_turkish_02.gif.gif" width="20" height="14" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_arabic.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_bahasa_id.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_chinese_06.gif.gif" width="20" height="12" />&nbsp;     <img src="/fileadmin/_migrated/RTE/RTEmagicC_flag_japanese_06.gif.gif" width="20" height="13" /></p><h2>Two Versions for Different Requirements</h2><p><span class="mark2"><span style="font-family:'QuicksandBold',Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:11pt">VSIS ConfTool</span></span><br /> The <strong>standard version VSIS ConfTool</strong> was designed for smaller events with up to 150 participants. It is an open/shared-source system available under different licenses. VSIS ConfTool&nbsp;is geared towards academic organizers of small, non-commercial events.&nbsp;The system <a href="/en/features.html" title="Opens internal link in current window">features only&nbsp;basic functions</a> and&nbsp;is offered without support and for local installation only.&nbsp;We offer a <a href="/en/about-conftool/vsis-conftool-license.html" title="Opens internal link in current window">free license on request</a>.</p><p><span class="mark2"><span style="font-family:'QuicksandBold',Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:11pt">ConfTool Pro</span></span><br /> The <strong>professional version ConfTool Pro</strong> has substantially more features, is more flexible and also suitable for events with many participants, several contribution types and/or sub-events. ConfTool Pro is offered as a hosted service with full technical support. The fee depends on the requirements and the size of your event. Contact us for a quote: <a href="javascript:linkTo_UnCryptMailto(%27kygjrm8pcoscqrqYamldrmmj%2Clcr%27);" title="Opens internal link in current window" class="mail">requests<span style='color:#600000'>&#064;</span>conftool<span style='color:#000080'>&#046;</span>net</a></p><h2>ConfTool Pro - Your Benefits</h2><p>ConfTool Pro offers a number of advantages that will help you to organize your event as efficiently as possible:</p><ul><li>Hosted software solution with full&nbsp;setup and professional support for the configuration and use of the software</li><li>Customazible submission and review forms</li><li>Scheduling of the conference program</li><li>Enhanced export options</li><li>Invitation option for &nbsp;authors, participants, reviewers and program committee members</li><li>Enhanced payment options (e.g., PayPal, Skrill (Moneybookers) and optional modules for credit card gateways)</li></ul><p>You can access online demos for <a href="/en/demo_installations.html#c8" title="Opens internal link in current window">VSIS ConfTool Standard</a> and <a href="/en/demo_installations.html#c386" title="Opens internal link in current window">ConfTool Pro</a>&nbsp;to get an impression of the system.</p><p>For further information, we are happy to assist you. Please send us an e-mail to <a href="javascript:linkTo_UnCryptMailto(%27kygjrm8pcoscqrqYamldrmmj%2Clcr%27);" title="Opens window for sending email">requests<span style='color:#600000'>&#064;</span>conftool<span style='color:#000080'>&#046;</span>net</a> or <a href="/en/about-conftool/contact.html#c38" title="Opens internal link in current window">call us</a>.</p></div>



